    "description": "Weds Co., Ltd., together with its subsidiaries, engages in the automobile-related wholesale business in Japan. It operates through Automobile Related Sales Business, Logistics Business, Automotive Retail Business, and Welfare segments. The company is involved in the wholesale business, such as after-sales service of automobile parts, automobile wheels, and car accessory parts; manufactures steel wheels; sale of automobile wheel parts; manufacture and sale of high-end aluminum wheels; and logistics business, including storage and loading of wheels and other original products. It also provides warehousing services; wheels and car accessory parts retail business; welfare services for the elderly; and operates as a real estate rental company. The company was formerly known as Nippo Co., Ltd. and changed its name to Weds Co., Ltd. in November 1973. Weds Co., Ltd. was founded in 1965 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan."
